divs: Sighting DetailsI took the dog out in the back yard to potty at about 10pm. I felt the urge to look up and to my right (west). I saw a diamond shaped object bobing in the air. It was very bright and changed colors. I got my wife and daughter to look but they were sceptical. To make sure I was seeing what I thought I was I got 2 neighbors to look. We all saw the same thing. While watching the ufo I believe it made a comercial airplane change course. Shortly after that I believe a small airplane went to intercept the ufo. I can't say for sure because by that time the ufo was barely in sight. It had moved a great distance to the west. Total view time 15-20 min. I did use high powered binoculores to view the ufo as did my neighbors. I know for a fact it was not a conventinal aircraft of any kind. Lets just say I didn't sleep well that night. Seeing is believing. Sighting took place on 5-3-09 Between 10 and 10:30pm in Brooklyn Park MN near West Broadway and 85th Ave I lost sight of the ufo when it traveled west out of sight.
